			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">Question</span>: I've installed Textual Confirmation. However, any answer is accepted. What is wrong?
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Answer</span>: Most likely, the problem is that the string &quot;tc_hook_register();&quot; was inserted to a wrong position in the file &quot;includes/usercp_register.php&quot;. There are a lot of curly braces, which sometimes cause confusion.
<br />

<br />
For example, you might have the tc_hook_register(); before the end brackets:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">$error = TRUE;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$error_msg .= &#40; &#40; isset&#40;$error_msg&#41; &#41; ? '&lt;br /&gt;' &#58; '' &#41; . $lang&#91;'Fields_empty'&#93;;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;tc_hook_register&#40;&#41;;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#125;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
Instead of after:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">$error = TRUE;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$error_msg .= &#40; &#40; isset&#40;$error_msg&#41; &#41; ? '&lt;br /&gt;' &#58; '' &#41; . $lang&#91;'Fields_empty'&#93;;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#125;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;tc_hook_register&#40;&#41;;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
<br />
Do you love our tools? <a href="https://www.plimus.com/jsp/buynow.jsp?contractId=1671485" target="_blank" class="postlink">Please sponsor</a> further development!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
